State Tournament Practice Party

Rolla High School,
900 Bulldog Run, Rolla, MO 65401 United States

Rolla Robotics will again host a practice party for teams competing in the Missouri State Championship Tournament. Our practice field will be available for testing and it’s a great way to get a head start on scouting your competition and potential alliance partners for the tournament.

Missouri State Championship

March 7

All three Rolla teams will compete on March 7th at the Missouri State Championship for FTC. Top finishers will advance to the North Super-Regional Championship in Des Moines, IA to be held March 26-28, 2015.

April 2015

FIRST World Championship

April 22 - April 25
St. Louis Union Station,
1820 Market St., St. Louis, MO 63103 United States
+ Google Map

Advancing teams from the FTC North Super-regional will compete at the World Championship in St. Louis. In past years the World Championship has been held at the Edward Jones Dome and the Americas Center. Due to the growth of FIRST, the event is expanding to multiple venues this year. St. Louis Union Station will be the home base for FTC competition this year.
